üßæ 10. Conclusion

The web application demonstrates severe SQL Injection vulnerabilities allowing:

Full data extraction

Unauthorized data manipulation

Schema modification

Privilege escalation

Log deletion (availability compromise)

Without remediation, these vulnerabilities put the system at critical risk.

Securing the application requires immediate implementation of safe coding practices and database hardening.
